<img src=http://24.116.149.140/tux.jpg height=120 width=120></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/upalimaxsceleris.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Palimax Sceleris</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Local Resident</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/10/02 5:49:29 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=805.topic&index=1>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Planes and Guns</span><hr size=1> You can't seriously tell me you can't think of a SINGLE reason that it'd be bad to have a gun on a plane?<br>
