Guildleader: <a href=http://www.guildvision.org>Vision</a>, Grandmaster <a href=http://www.base-nine.org/available_tinkering_items.htm>Tinkerer</a></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#383838><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub42.ezboard.com/ufeuerfaust.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Feuerfaust</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Boardfellow</span><br> <font color=#ff0000>(1/10/02 7:15:04 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub42.ezboard.com/fayonaerofrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=805.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://24.116.149.140/burt.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Planes and Guns</span><hr size=1> Well, what are the cons for you Palimax?  Cost is one that I saw mentioned, and though was valid, and I didn't really have a decent counter for (aside from "What cost is too much for 100+ lives?", but that's trite.)<br>
