<br>
1. Who will watch the watchers?  I dunno about you, but I know some flight attendants in RL- no way in hell I trust them with a gun, training or not, they're freaks.  While I'm sure that pilots are more reliable than that, there are bound to be a few less than perfect examples out there.<br>
<br>
